Name: Dino Delivery
About the game: Collect letters, solve puzzles, and uncover the mystery of the missing eggs - all while riding a dinosaur! In a land where people and dinosaurs live side-by-side, a rampaging carnotaurus has stormed the post office. There may be more to the situation than meets the eye, however. It's up to junior postmaster Pip and his best dino bud Parcel to recover the scattered letters and figure out what could have made a dinosaur so angry. Features: Cooperate with your adorable dinosaur Parcel to solve puzzles. Use your trusty berry slingshot to shoot objects and tell Parcel where to go. Explore the vibrant town of Cretaceous Cliffs. Interact with over 10 quirky NPCs who will help you on your adventure. In addition to collecting letters, deliver them to the right mailboxes and collect trinkets for Parcel. About Development This game was developed as a student project at DigiPen Institute of Technology and was created for educational purposes only. Please check out our publisher page for more information.
